text: == Events == * Tiberius and Germanicus are Roman Consuls. * A vexillatio (sub- unit) of Legio III Augusta is destroyed by an ambush in Africa. * The German chieftain Arminius destroys the kingdom of the Marcomanni. * In India, the Indo-Parthians control Taxila. * Caiaphas becomes the high priest of Jerusalem. ==Deaths== * Ovid, Roman poet (or 17) Category:10s
